        "score": 5,
        "is_accepted": true,
        "last_activity_date": 1527030530,
        "creation_date": 1527030530,
        "body": "<p><a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/technotes/guides/language/underscores-literals.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Java allows<\/a> numeric literals with <code>_<\/code> for better readability. <\/p>\n\n<p>For example:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>int i = 10_000;\nfloat pi =      3.14_15F;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
